    "description": {
      "value": "<h3 id=\"a-living-source\">A Living Source</h3><p>The Sōzō clan hails from the Land of Carrots, with ancestral roots stretching back centuries. Known for their unique orange hair, green eyes, and revitalizing chakra, Sōzō clansmen possess a special dojutsu called the Naibugan. This visual prowess synergizes with their extraordinary abilities in manipulating medical release chakra.</p><h4 id=\"s-z-traits\">Sōzō Traits</h4><hr /><ul><li><strong>Ability Score Increase:</strong> +2 Wis, +1 Int</li><li><strong>Speed:</strong> Your base walking speed is 30 feet</li><li><strong>Skill Proficiencies:</strong> Medicine, Perception</li><li><strong>Medical Affinity:</strong> You gain the ability to learn jutsu with the Medical keyword.</li></ul>",
